skittles
skittles
[treated as sing.] Brit. informal chess that is not played seriously.
→ skittle
————————
skittles
[treated as sing.] a game played with wooden pins, typically nine in number, set up at the end of an alley to be bowled down with a wooden ball or disc.
→ skittle

sentences.en: For Sam, college was beer and skittles. He wasted a lot of time and money.
